				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-M%E1%BB%99ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/Chu-trung-v%E1%BB%8Dng-B%C3%B4-C%C3%B4-h%C3%A3n-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m/poem-SUKMkrh5ZU7A5JN_H_7pzw">Chu trung vọng Bô Cô hãn hữu cảm - 舟中望逋姑捍有感</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-M%E1%BB%99ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-X8HbPHDbusd0AT4a_Lx-4A">Vũ Mộng Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-V%C4%A9nh/D%E1%BA%A1-b%C3%A1n-l%E1%BA%A1c/poem-uCmvnDFijtx2_QPV_fQ0sw">Dạ bán lạc - 夜半樂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-V%C4%A9nh/author-ODOFEl8xHVsWXQUPgj9Ktg">Liễu Vĩnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/H%C3%A0n-bi/poem-aUyDGdFMte6NkDc2IR5eWA">Hàn bi - 韓碑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BB%B9-Bi-h%C3%A0nh/poem-KDeXacIPup13jcPdFEiINQ">Mỹ Bi hành - 渼陂行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-l%C3%A2u-xu%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-55fF62i8qAKasipDKsI8ZA">Ngọc lâu xuân kỳ 1 - 玉樓春其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%82u-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tu/author-Rh6zapU4AwLAuhG1Xl_FMw">Âu Dương Tu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%83n-Anh/Oanh-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-t%E1%BB%B1-Xu%C3%A2n-v%C3%A3n-c%E1%BA%A3m-ho%C3%A0i/poem-LcZO7umLHbomc4hN4qKm7A">Oanh đề tự - Xuân vãn cảm hoài - 鶯啼序－春晚感懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-V%C4%83n-Anh/author-to-UkdFjJeg6pwDSfG5oNA">Ngô Văn Anh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-Kh%C3%B4ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%93/T%C3%A1i-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/poem-MY0fsHhB1aZbLrdFloVv5A">Tái thượng - 塞上</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net